data.description: **Open House Cancelled**You will not want to miss your opportunity to tour this quintessential cottage-style contemporary cutie in sought-after Meadows in Lake Linganore.  Absolutely super location with flat fenced backyard & multiple decks for fabulous outdoor enjoyment.  You'll love the updated kitchen with granite counters, breakfast bar & custom lighting. Relax in the charming living room enhanced with exposed beams, wood floors and cozy wood-burning fireplace. Main level primary bedroom/full bath with additional adorably large bedrooms/full bath upstairs. Lower level has recreation area & bonus/office room with extra storage and rough-in for future full bath. Spacious 1-car garage plus plenty of extra parking in the long driveway.  This perfect package includes a 1-year warranty.  Take advantage of all the amenities in Lake Lingnore for that "vacation-feel" all year long. You'll never want to leave this home sweet home!
